Shuffle Master to sell machines in Nevada . Shuffle Master Inc said Monday it received approval from Nevada regulators to market its new software in a video gaming machine . The company said the software improves the Let It Ride Bonus Video game by increasing the frequency of winning hands , offering improved help functions and delivering more player - friendly graphics . Shuffle Master said it plans to begin selling machines made by Bally Gaming International Inc by the end of the month . Shuffle Master provides products and services to the casino industry . ( ( Chicago newsdesk ( 312 ) 408 - 8787 ) ) 
